Available Tools: start_instance | stop_instance | restart_instance | terminate_instance
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "instance_id": "string", "region": "string" }
Response Schema: { "instance_id": "string", "state": "string", "message": "string" }
---
Question: Restart the web server instance i-0a1b2c3d4e5f in us-east-1 for scheduled maintenance.
Call: { "func_call": "restart_instance", "instance_id": "i-0a1b2c3d4e5f", "region": "us-east-1" }
Response: { "instance_id": "i-0a1b2c3d4e5f", "state": "rebooting", "message": "Instance restart initiated for scheduled maintenance." }

Question: Terminate the old batch processing node i-9z8y7x6w5v in eu-west-2 as part of the scale-down event.
Call: { "func_call": "terminate_instance", "instance_id": "i-9z8y7x6w5v", "region": "eu-west-2" }
Response: { "instance_id": "i-9z8y7x6w5v", "state": "shutting-down", "message": "Instance termination successful due to scale-down." }

Question: We need to apply kernel updates; please restart instance i-1122334455 in ap-southeast-1.
Call: { "func_call": "restart_instance", "instance_id": "i-1122334455", "region": "ap-southeast-1" }
Response: { "instance_id": "i-1122334455", "state": "rebooting", "message": "Instance rebooting to apply kernel updates." }

Question: The dev environment instance i-dev001 in us-west-1 is no longer needed; terminate it immediately.
Call: { "func_call": "terminate_instance", "instance_id": "i-dev001", "region": "us-west-1" }
Response: { "instance_id": "i-dev001", "state": "shutting-down", "message": "Development instance terminated successfully." }

